ypto, forex, and economic topics.\",\n      \"params\": [\n        {\n          \"name\": \"function\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": true,\n          \"description\": {\n            \"en\": \"The function to call. In this case, NEWS_SENTIMENT\"\n          },\n          \"enum\": [\n            \"NEWS_SENTIMENT\"\n          ]\n        },\n        {\n          \"name\": \"tickers\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": false,\n          \"description\": {\n            \"en\": \"Comma-separated list of stock/crypto/forex symbols to filter articles by (e.g., AAPL,CRYPTO:BTC).\"\n          }\n        },\n        {\n          \"name\": \"topics\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": false,\n          \"description\": {\n            \"en\": \"Comma-separated list of topics to filter by.\"\n          },\n          \"enum\": [\n            \"blockchain\",\n            \"earnings\",\n            \"ipo\",\n            \"mergers_and_acquisitions\",\n            \"financial_markets\",\n            \"economy_fiscal\",\n            \"economy_monetary\",\n            \"economy_macro\",\n            \"energy_transportation\",\n            \"finance\",\n            \"life_sciences\",\n            \"manufacturing\",\n            \"real_estate\",\n            \"retail_wholesale\",\n            \"technology\"\n          ]\n        },\n        {\n          \"name\": \"time_from\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": false,\n          \"description\": {\n            \"en\": \"Start time in YYYYMMDDTHHMM format (e.g., 20220410T0130).\"\n          }\n        },\n        {\n          \"name\": \"time_to\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": false,\n          \"description\": {\n            \"en\": \"End time in YYYYMMDDTHHMM format.\"\n          }\n        },\n        {\n          \"name\": \"sort\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": false,\n          \"description\": {\n            \"en\": \"Sorting method for results.\"\n          },\n          \"enum\": [\n            \"LATEST\",\n            \"EARLIEST\",\n            \"RELEVANCE\"\n          ]\n        },\n        {\n          \"name\": \"limit\",\n          \"type\": \"integer\",\n          \"required\": false,\n          \"description\": {\n            \"en\": \"Maximum number of results (up to 1000).\"\n          }\n        }\n      ],\n      \"examples\": {\n        \"sample_parameters\": {\n          \"function\": \"NEWS_SENTIMENT\"\n        }\n      },\n      \"provider_description\": \"Alpha Vantage provides realtime and historical financial market data through a set of powerful and developer-friendly data APIs and spreadsheets. From traditional asset classes (e.g., stocks, ETFs, mutual funds) to economic indicators, from foreign exchange rates to commodities, from fundamental data to technical indicators, Alpha Vantage is your one-stop-shop for enterprise-grade global market data delivered through cloud-based APIs, MCP servers, spreadsheets, and more.\",\n      \"stats\": {\n        \"avg_execution_time_ms\": 538.66,\n        \"success_rate\": 0.734\n      }\n    },\n    {\n      \"tool_id\": \"qveris_social.x_domain_hot_events_v1\",\n      \"name\": \"X Domain Hot Events Today\",\n      \"description\": \"Summarize today's hot events on X/Twitter for a domain: fetch new posts then use LLM to summarize events and return event list with post ids.\",\n      \"params\": [\n        {\n          \"name\": \"domains\",\n          \"type\": \"array\",\n          \"required\": false,\n          \"description\": {\n            \"en\": \"Domain(s) to summarize\",\n            \"zh\": \"要总结的领域\"\n          },\n          \"enum\": [\n            \"AI\",\n            \"Finance\",\n            \"Crypto\",\n            \"Tech\",\n            \"Science\"\n          ]\n        }\n      ],\n      \"provider_description\": \"Social media monitoring and analysis skills\",\n      \"stats\": {\n        \"avg_execution_time_ms\": 22032.14,\n        \"success_rate\": 1\n      },\n      \"skill_package_url\": \"https://qveris.ai/api/v1/skills/qveris_social.x_domain_hot_events_v1/package\",\n      \"skill_type\": \"package\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"tool_id\": \"qveris_social.x_domain_new_posts_v1\",\n      \"name\": \"X Domain New Posts Today\",\n      \"description\": \"Search today's new posts from domain experts (KOLs) on X/Twitter with full fields: text, images, media, metrics. Supports AI, Finance, Crypto, Tech, Science.\",\n      \"params\": [\n        {\n          \"name\": \"domains\",\n          \"type\": \"array\",\n          \"required\": false,\n          \"description\": {\n            \"en\": \"Domains to query\",\n            \"zh\": \"要查询的领域\"\n          },\n          \"enum\": [\n            \"AI\",\n            \"Finance\",\n            \"Crypto\",\n            \"Tech\",\n            \"Science\"\n          ]\n        },\n        {\n          \"name\": \"limit\",\n          \"type\": \"integer\",\n          \"required\": false,\n          \"description\": null\n        }\n      ],\n      \"provider_description\": \"Social media monitoring and analysis skills\",\n      \"stats\": {\n        \"avg_execution_time_ms\": 7737.01,\n        \"success_rate\": 1\n      },\n      \"skill_package_url\": \"https://qveris.ai/api/v1/skills/qveris_social.x_domain_new_posts_v1/package\",\n      \"skill_type\": \"package\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"tool_id\": \"gdelt-data.doc.tonechart.retrieve.v2.a7b24341\",\n      \"name\": \"Retrieve Tone Chart\",\n      \"description\": \"Generates a histogram showing the distribution of article tones (from extremely negative to extremely positive) for articles mentioning a specific query over the last 3 months.\",\n      \"params\": [\n        {\n          \"name\": \"query\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": true,\n          \"description\": {\n            \"en\": \"Search query phrase\"\n          }\n        },\n        {\n          \"name\": \"mode\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": true,\n          \"description\": {\n            \"en\": \"API operation mode\"\n          },\n          \"enum\": [\n            \"tonechart\"\n          ]\n        }\n      ],\n      \"examples\": {\n        \"sample_parameters\": {\n          \"mode\": \"tonechart\",\n          \"query\": \"climate change\"\n        }\n      },\n      \"provider_description\": \"The Global Database of Events, Language, and Tone (GDELT) monitors the world's broadcast, print, and web news from nearly every corner of every country in over 100 languages and identifies the people, locations, organizations, counts, themes, sources, emotions, quotes, images and events driving our global society every second of every day. GDELT 2.0 updates every 15 minutes with new features including realtime translation of 65 languages and measurement of over 2,300 emotions and themes.\",\n      \"stats\": {\n        \"avg_execution_time_ms\": 19242.44,\n        \"success_rate\": 0.077\n      }\n    },\n    {\n      \"tool_id\": \"alphavantage.news_sentiment.retrieve.v1.7aca3c4a\",\n      \"name\": \"Retrieve Market News & Sentiment\",\n      \"description\": \"Returns live and historical market news & sentiment data from premier news outlets around the world, covering stocks, cryptocurrencies, forex, and various financial topics.\",\n      \"params\": [\n        {\n          \"name\": \"function\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": true,\n          \"description\": {\n            \"en\": \"The function name.\"\n          },\n          \"enum\": [\n            \"NEWS_SENTIMENT\"\n          ]\n        },\n        {\n          \"name\": \"tickers\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": false,\n          \"description\": {\n            \"en\": \"Comma-separated list of stock/crypto/forex symbols (e.g., COIN,CRYPTO:BTC,FOREX:USD). Filters articles that mention all listed tickers.\"\n          }\n        },\n        {\n          \"name\": \"topics\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": false,\n          \"description\": {\n            \"en\": \"Comma-separated list of topics. Articles must cover all listed topics.\"\n          },\n          \"enum\": [\n            \"blockchain\",\n            \"earnings\",\n            \"ipo\",\n            \"mergers_and_acquisitions\",\n            \"financial_markets\",\n            \"economy_fiscal\",\n            \"economy_monetary\",\n            \"economy_macro\",\n            \"energy_transportation\",\n            \"finance\",\n            \"life_sciences\",\n            \"manufacturing\",\n            \"real_estate\",\n            \"retail_wholesale\",\n            \"technology\"\n          ]\n        },\n        {\n          \"name\": \"time_from\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": false,\n          \"description\": {\n            \"en\": \"Start time in YYYYMMDDTHHMM format (e.g., 20220410T0130).\"\n          }\n        },\n        {\n          \"name\": \"time_to\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": false,\n          \"description\": {\n            \"en\": \"End time in YYYYMMDDTHHMM format.\"\n          }\n        },\n        {\n          \"name\": \"sort\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": false,\n          \"description\": {\n            \"en\": \"Sorting method.\"\n          },\n          \"enum\": [\n            \"LATEST\",\n            \"EARLIEST\",\n            \"RELEVANCE\"\n          ]\n        },\n        {\n          \"name\": \"limit\",\n          \"type\": \"integer\",\n          \"required\": false,\n          \"description\": {\n            \"en\": \"Maximum number of results (up to 1000).\"\n          }\n        }\n      ],\n      \"examples\": {\n        \"sample_parameters\": {\n          \"function\": \"NEWS_SENTIMENT\"\n        }\n      },\n      \"provider_description\": \"Alpha Vantage provides realtime and historical financial market data through a set of powerful and developer-friendly data APIs and spreadsheets. From traditional asset classes (e.g., stocks, ETFs, mutual funds) to economic indicators, from foreign exchange rates to commodities, from fundamental data to technical indicators, Alpha Vantage is your one-stop-shop for enterprise-grade global market data delivered through cloud-based APIs, MCP servers, spreadsheets, and more.\",\n      \"stats\": {\n        \"avg_execution_time_ms\": 672.29,\n        \"success_rate\": 0.893\n      }\n    },\n    {\n      \"tool_id\": \"coingecko.search.trending.retrieve.v3.548c6bf0\",\n      \"name\": \"Trending Search List\",\n      \"description\": \"This endpoint allows you **query trending search coins, NFTs and categories on CoinGecko in the last 24 hours**\",\n      \"provider_description\": \"CoinGecko API provides onchain DEX data across 250+ blockchain networks, 1,700+ decentralized exchanges (DEXes), and 15M+ tokens, powered by GeckoTerminal. It offers price feeds, market data, metadata, and historical data of crypto assets, NFTs, and exchanges. Includes WebSocket API for real-time data.\",\n      \"stats\": {\n        \"avg_execution_time_ms\": 0,\n        \"success_rate\": 0\n      }\n    }\n  ],\n  \"search_id\": \"3995db6a-ef6b-4f92-a40a-1ad959bf7970\",\n  \"elapsed_time_ms\": 203.72\n}","cwd":"/Users/lynch/.openclaw/workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1772592183982}}
{"type":"message","id":"01e382b0","parentId":"c455d74a","timestamp":"2026-03-04T02:43:12.156Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"我看到有 Alpha Vantage 的新闻情绪 API，它的结果中包含 \"relevance\" 分数。但用户明确要求使用 Finnhub。\n\n让我尝试用不同的方式来执行 Finnhub 的工具。问题可能在于 QVeris 脚本的参数解析。让我检查一下脚本的用法。","thinkingSignature":"01fce3887afd9483808e4f73398f376554639189ba5d5749b1c4bf8f9d1367c7"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_zukhslf8zd5k_1","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"~/.openclaw/workspace/scripts/qveris_tool.mjs"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.5","usage":{"input":17085,"output":95,"cacheRead":13984,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":31164,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1772592183985}}
{"type":"message","id":"444e8453","parentId":"01e382b0","timestamp":"2026-03-04T02:43:12.165Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_zukhslf8zd5k_1","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"#!/usr/bin/env node\n\nconst API_BASE = 'https://qveris.ai/api/v1';\nconst API_KEY = process.env.QVERIS_API_KEY;\n\nasync function search(query, limit = 10) {\n  const res = await fetch(`${API_BASE}/search`, {\n    method: 'POST',\n    headers: {\n      'Content-Type': 'application/json',\n      'Authorization': `Bearer ${API_KEY}`\n    },\n    body: JSON.stringify({ query, limit })\n  });\n  const data = await res.json();\n  return data;\n}\n\nasync function execute(toolId, params, searchId = null) {\n  const res = await fetch(`${API_BASE}/tools/execute`, {\n    method: 'POST',\n    headers: {\n      'Content-Type': 'application/json',\n      'Authorization': `Bearer ${API_KEY}`\n    },\n    body: JSON.stringify({ tool_id: toolId, params, search_id: searchId })\n  });\n  const data = await res.json();\n  return data;\n}\n\nasync function getByIds(...ids) {\n  const res = await fetch(`${API_BASE}/tools/get-by-ids`, {\n    method: 'POST',\n    headers: {\n      'Content-Type': 'application/json',\n      'Authorization': `Bearer ${API_KEY}`\n    },\n    body: JSON.stringify({ ids })\n  });\n  const data = await res.json();\n  return data;\n}\n\nconst cmd = process.argv[2];\nconst args = process.argv.slice(3);\n\nasync function main() {\n  try {\n    if (cmd === 'search') {\n      const query = args[0];\n      const limit = args.includes('--limit') ? parseInt(args[args.indexOf('--limit') + 1]) : 10;\n      const result = await search(query, limit);\n      console.log(JSON.stringify(result, null, 2));\n    } else if (cmd === 'execute') {\n      const toolId = args[0];\n      const searchIdIdx = args.indexOf('--search-id');\n      const searchId = searchIdIdx > -1 ? args[searchIdIdx + 1] : null;\n      const paramsIdx = args.indexOf('--params');\n      const params = paramsIdx > -1 ? JSON.parse(args[paramsIdx + 1]) : {};\n      const result = await execute(toolId, params, searchId);\n      console.log(JSON.stringify(result, null, 2));\n    } else if (cmd === 'get-by-ids') {\n      const result = await getByIds(...args.filter(a => !a.startsWith('--')));\n      console.log(JSON.stringify(result, null, 2));\n    } else {\n      console.error('Unknown command:', cmd);\n      process.exit(1);\n    }\n  } catch (err) {\n    console.error('Error:', err.message);\n    process.exit(1);\n  }\n}\n\nmain();\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1772592192163}}
