{"type":"message","id":"c3ab8927","parentId":"75e03f13","timestamp":"2026-03-04T02:46:24.626Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"QVeris API 存在严重问题。让我尝试直接调用 Finnhub API 而不是通过 QVeris，或者尝试用 web_fetch/web_search 来获取 Finnhub 的新闻数据。但用户明确要求使用 QVeris finnhub。\n\n让我检查一下是否有其他可用的工具或者看看 QVeris 的状态。也许我需要等待一段时间再试。\n\n实际上，让我换一个思路 - 用户要求的是 Finnhub 财经新闻，热度≥80。Finnhub 本身可能不提供热度分数，但也许可以通过其他方式获取。\n\n让我先尝试使用 QVeris 的 X Domain Hot Topics 功能来获取财经热门话题，这可能更符合用户对\"热度\"的需求。","thinkingSignature":"502882dfa02a617df19e50cb95aa8873c59ef922bdf869506b82c99be62abb1b"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_kfnim6ehzl9v_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"curl -s -X POST https://qveris.ai/api/v1/search \\\n  -H \"Content-Type: application/json\" \\\n  -H \"Authorization: Bearer $QVERIS_API_KEY\" \\\n  -d '{\"query\": \"qveris X hot finance topics\", \"limit\": 3}'","timeout":30}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.5","usage":{"input":23066,"output":232,"cacheRead":13984,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":37282,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1772592375116}}
