ct your investment.\\\\n\\\\nInvestor Checklist\\\\n\\\\nQuick Assessment\\\\n\\\\n⚖️ Price vs Analyst Target: At about $263.75, Apple trades roughly 10% below the consensus price target of $293.29, which sits within the analyst range of $205 to $350. ⚖️ Simply Wall St Valuation: Apple is described as trading close to estimated fair value, so the current price does not screen as a clear discount or premium on this model. ✅ Recent Momentum: The 30 day return is about 1.6%, which is a mildly positive move as the new hardware cycle gets underway.\\\\n\\\\nThere is only one way to know the right time to buy, sell or hold Apple. Head to the Simply Wall St company report for the latest analysis of Apple's fair value.\\\\n\\\\nKey Considerations\\\\n\\\\n📊 This multi day refresh across iPhone, iPad, Mac, and Studio Display keeps Apple’s hardware ecosystem front and center, which is important given its role in driving usage of services and software. 📊 You might want to watch uptake of the M4 and M5 chips, AI focused features, and any commentary on how these devices influence revenue and earnings, which have been growing annually based on the provided figures. ⚠️ With a P/E of 32.88 versus an industry average of about 26.89, a key risk is that expectations embedded in the price may be high if the new products do not translate into the level of growth the market is anticipating.\\\\n\\\\nStory Continues\\\\n\\\\nDig Deeper\\\\n\\\\nFor the full picture including more risks and rewards, check out the complete Apple analysis. Alternatively, you can visit the community page for Apple to see how other investors believe this latest news will impact the company's narrative.\\\\n\\\\nThis article by Simply Wall St is general in nature. We provide commentary based on historical data and analyst forecasts only using an unbiased methodology and our articles are not intended to be financial advice. It does not constitute a recommendation to buy or sell any stock, and does not take account of your objectives, or your financial situation. We aim to bring you long-term focused analysis driven by fundamental data. Note that our analysis may not factor in the latest price-sensitive company announcements or qualitative material. Simply Wall St has no position in any stocks mentioned.\\\\n\\\\nCompanies discussed in this article include AAPL.\\\\n\\\\nHave feedback on this article? Concerned about the content? Get in touch with us directly. Alternatively, email editorial-team@simplywallst.com\\\\n\\\\nView Comments\\\", \\\"link\\\": \\\"https://finance.yahoo.com/news/apple-broad-hardware-refresh-puts-021224368.html\\\", \\\"symbols\\\": [\\\"AAPL.US\\\"], \\\"tags\\\": [\\\"AI\\\", \\\"EARNINGS\\\", \\\"HARDWARE\\\", \\\"PRICE TARGET\\\", \\\"PRICE-TARGET\\\", \\\"SEMICONDUCTORS\\\"], \\\"sentiment\\\": {\\\"polarity\\\": 0.99, \\\"neg\\\": 0.015, \\\"neu\\\": 0.912, \\\"pos\\\": 0.073}}, {\\\"date\\\": \\\"2026-03-04T02:11:00+00:00\\\", \\\"title\\\": \\\"Bragar Eagel &amp; Squire, P.C. Urges CoreWeave, Inc. (NASDAQ:CRWV) Stockholders with Large Losses to Contact the Firm Before March 13th\\\", \\\"content\\\": \\\"Bragar Eagel & Squire, P.C. Litigation Partner Brandon Walker Encourages Investors Who Suffered Losses In CoreWeave (CRWV) To Contact Him Directly To Discuss Their Options\\\\n\\\\nIf you purchased or acquired CoreWeave securities between March 28, 2025 and December 15, 2025, and would like to discuss your legal rights, call Bragar Eagel & Squire partner Brandon Walker or Melissa Fortunato directly at (212) 355-4648.\\\\n\\\\nClick here to participate in the action.\\\\n\\\\nNEW YORK, March  03, 2026  (GLOBE NEWSWIRE) --\\\\n\\\\nWhat’s Happening?\\\\n\\\\nBragar Eagel & Squire, P.C., a nationally recognized stockholder rights law firm, announces that a class action lawsuit has been filed against CoreWeave, Inc. (“CoreWeave” or the “Company”) (NASDAQ:CRWV) in the United States District Court for the District of New Jersey on behalf of all persons and entities who purchased or otherwise acquired CoreWeave securities between March 28, 2025 and December 15, 2025, both dates inclusive (the “Class Period”). Investors have until March 13, 2026 to apply to the Court to be appointed as lead plaintiff in the lawsuit.\\\\n\\\\nWhat are the Allegation Details?\\\\n\\\\nThe lawsuit alleges that Defendants issued false and misleading statements and/or failed to disclose that: (i) Defendants had overstated CoreWeave’s ability to meet customer demand for its service; (ii) Defendants materially understated the scope and severity of the risk that CoreWeave’s reliance on a single third-party data center supplier presented for CoreWeave’s ability to meet customer demand for its services; and (iii) the foregoing was reasonably likely to have a material negative impact on the Company’s revenue.\\\\n\\\\nWhat are the Next Steps?\\\\n\\\\nIf you purchased or otherwise acquired CoreWeave shares and suffered a loss, are a long-term stockholder, have information, would like to learn more about these claims, or have any questions concerning this announcement or your rights or interests with respect to these matters, please contact Brandon Walker or Melissa Fortunato by email at investigations@bespc.com, telephone at (212) 355-4648, or by filling out this contact form. There is no cost or obligation to you.\\\\n\\\\nAbout Bragar Eagel & Squire, P.C.:\\\\n\\\\nBragar Eagel & Squire, P.C. is a nationally recognized law firm with offices in New York, South Carolina, and California. The firm represents individual and institutional investors in securities, derivative, and commercial litigation as well as individuals in consumer protection and data privacy litigation. The firm has a nationwide practice and routinely handles cases in both federal and state courts. For more information about the firm, please visit www.bespc.com.  Attorney advertising.  Prior results do not guarantee similar outcomes.\\\\r\\\\nFollow us for updates on LinkedIn and Facebook, and keep up with other news by following Brandon Walker, Esq. on LinkedIn.\\\\n\\\\nContact Information:\\\\n\\\\nBragar Eagel & Squire, P.C.\\\\r\\\\nBrandon Walker, Esq.\\\\r\\\\nMelissa Fortunato, Esq.\\\\r\\\\n(212) 355-4648\\\\r\\\\ninvestigations@bespc.com\\\\r\\\\nwww.bespc.com\\\", \\\"link\\\": \\\"https://www.globenewswire.com/news-release/2026/03/04/3249018/0/en/Bragar-Eagel-Squire-P-C-Urges-CoreWeave-Inc-NASDAQ-CRWV-Stockholders-with-Large-Losses-to-Contact-the-Firm-Before-March-13th.html\\\", \\\"symbols\\\": [\\\"CRWV.US\\\"], \\\"tags\\\": [\\\"BES\\\", \\\"BRAGAR EAGEL & SQUIRE\\\", \\\"BRANDON WALKER\\\", \\\"CLASS ACTION\\\", \\\"CLASS-ACTION\\\", \\\"COMPLAINT\\\", \\\"COREWEAVE\\\", \\\"CRWV\\\", \\\"DROP\\\", \\\"FRAUD\\\", \\\"INSTITUTIONAL INVESTORS\\\", \\\"INVESTOR\\\", \\\"LAW & LEGAL ISSUES\\\", \\\"LAWSUIT\\\", \\\"LOSS\\\", \\\"SHARES\\\", \\\"STOCK\\\", \\\"STOCKHOLDER-RIGHTS\\\"], \\\"sentiment\\\": {\\\"polarity\\\": -0.617, \\\"neg\\\": 0.087, \\\"neu\\\": 0.837, \\\"pos\\\": 0.076}}, {\\\"date\\\": \\\"2026-03-04T02:10:12+00:00\\\", \\\"title\\\": \\\"Schneider Electric Links AI Data Center Growth With Sustainability Focus\\\", \\\"content\\\": \\\"Track your investments for FREE with Simply Wall St, the portfolio command center trusted by over 7 million individual investors worldwide.\\\\n\\\\nSchneider Electric, SK Telecom and Supermicro agreed to work together on modular AI data center solutions, targeting more scalable and efficient AI computing infrastructure. Schneider Electric also received an award recognizing its leadership in sustainable procurement practices.\\\\n\\\\nFor investors watching ENXTPA:SU, these moves add fresh context around a share price of €253.55 and a 3 year return of 72.9% and a 5 year return of 122.6%. The company is already well known for its role in energy management and automation, and this new AI data center focus broadens that industrial and digital footprint.\\\\n\\\\nThe tie up on AI data centers and the recognition for sustainable procurement both relate to how Schneider Electric is positioning itself in areas that matter for long term infrastructure and ESG minded capital. As these projects and practices develop, they may influence how you think about the balance between growth opportunities and sustainability credentials in any broader view of ENXTPA:SU.\\\\n\\\\nStay updated on the most important news stories for Schneider Electric by adding it to your watchlist or portfolio. Alternatively, explore our Community to discover new perspectives on Schneider Electric.ENXTPA:SU Earnings & Revenue Growth as at Mar 2026\\\\n\\\\nWe've flagged 1 risk for Schneider Electric. See which could impact your investment.\\\\n\\\\nThe AI data center partnership brings Schneider Electric closer to the fast growing compute build out, while the procurement award highlights how the company is trying to keep sustainability embedded in that growth. In practical terms, Schneider Electric contributes power, cooling and modular infrastructure, while SK Telecom and Supermicro bring AI workload expertise and servers. For you as an investor, this links the company’s traditional strengths in electrical equipment to a concrete use case in AI infrastructure, an area that also matters for peers such as ABB and Siemens.\\\\n\\\\nHow This Fits Into The Schneider Electric Narrative\\\\n\\\\nThe move into modular AI data centers lines up with the narrative’s focus on data center demand and digital services as key drivers for Schneider Electric’s long term earnings profile. The procurement award and increased AI focus also come with execution demands. This ties back to the narrative’s point that heavy inv\",\"content_schema\":{\"$schema\":\"http://json-schema.org/schema#\",\"type\":\"array\",\"items\":{\"type\":\"object\",\"properties\":{\"date\":{\"type\":\"string\"},\"title\":{\"type\":\"string\"},\"content\":{\"type\":\"string\"},\"link\":{\"type\":\"string\"},\"symbols\":{\"type\":\"array\",\"items\":{\"type\":\"string\"}},\"tags\":{\"type\":\"array\",\"items\":{\"type\":\"string\"}},\"sentiment\":{\"anyOf\":[{\"type\":\"null\"},{\"type\":\"object\",\"properties\":{\"polarity\":{\"type\":\"number\"},\"neg\":{\"type\":\"number\"},\"neu\":{\"type\":\"number\"},\"pos\":{\"type\":\"number\"}},\"required\":[\"neg\",\"neu\",\"polarity\",\"pos\"]}]}},\"required\":[\"content\",\"date\",\"link\",\"sentiment\",\"symbols\",\"tags\",\"title\"]}}},\"success\":true,\"elapsed_time_ms\":2733.04,\"cost\":6.5}","cwd":"/Users/lynch/.openclaw/workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1772592550948}}
{"type":"message","id":"948d83c7","parentId":"c4279e3a","timestamp":"2026-03-04T02:49:34.372Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"太好了！EODHD 的新闻 API 可以工作！我获取到了很多财经新闻。现在我需要检查这些新闻是否有热度分数。从返回的数据来看，有 `sentiment` 字段（包含 polarity, neg, neu, pos），但没有明显的\"热度\"分数。让我检查一下返回的数据中是否有其他字段可以代表热度。\n\n从数据来看：\n- 有 `date` - 日期\n- 有 `title` - 标题\n- 有 `content` - 内容\n- 有 `link` - 链接\n- 有 `symbols` - 相关股票代码\n- 有 `tags` - 标签\n- 有 `sentiment` - 情绪分数\n\n但是没有\"热度\"或\"relevance\"分数。用户要求的是热度≥80，这可能是指：\n1. 相关性分数 (relevance)\n2. 热度分数 (hotness)\n3. 或者是某种特定指标\n\n让我查看一下是否有其他字段或者看看完整的返回数据。从返回的数据中，我看到了 `sentiment` 字段，它的 `polarity` 值范围看起来是从 -1 到 1。这不是热度。\n\n让我看看是否有其他 API 可以获取热度分数。也许 Finnhub 的新闻 API 有不同的数据格式。或者我可以使用 X Domain Hot Topics 来获取热门话题。\n\n但是用户明确要求 Finnhub。让我再次尝试 Finnhub API，或者看看是否有其他工具可以提供热度数据。\n\n\nAlpha Vantage 的 NEWS_SENTIMENT API 有 `relevance` 字段，我可以尝试用它来筛选热度≥80的新闻。","thinkingSignature":"8efb10218344ef514c458fc01a2a640c5fbf74be127e73ad0b30c3097cf77cc6"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_20cn348m5ikt_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"curl -s -X POST https://qveris.ai/api/v1/search \\\n  -H \"Content-Type: application/json\" \\\n  -H \"Authorization: Bearer $QVERIS_API_KEY\" \\\n  -d '{\"query\": \"Alpha Vantage NEWS_SENTIMENT relevance\", \"limit\": 3}'","timeout":30}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.5","usage":{"input":35009,"output":406,"cacheRead":13984,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":49399,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1772592550953}}
{"type":"message","id":"ac394f9f","parentId":"948d83c7","timestamp":"2026-03-04T02:49:40.206Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_20cn348m5ikt_1","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"{\"query\":\"Alpha Vantage NEWS_SENTIMENT relevance\",\"total\":3,\"results\":[{\"tool_id\":\"alphavantage.news_sentiment.query.v1.7aca3c4a\",\"name\":\"Market News & Sentiment\",\"description\":\"Returns live and historical market news & sentiment data from global news outlets covering stocks, crypto, forex, and economic topics.\",\"params\":[{\"name\":\"function\",\"type\":\"string\",\"required\":true,\"description\":{\"en\":\"The function to call. In this case, NEWS_SENTIMENT\"},\"enum\":[\"NEWS_SENTIMENT\"]},{\"name\":\"tickers\",\"type\":\"string\",\"required\":false,\"description\":{\"en\":\"Comma-separated list of stock/crypto/forex symbols to filter articles by (e.g., AAPL,CRYPTO:BTC).\"}},{\"name\":\"topics\",\"type\":\"string\",\"required\":false,\"description\":{\"en\":\"Comma-separated list of topics to filter by.\"},\"enum\":[\"blockchain\",\"earnings\",\"ipo\",\"mergers_and_acquisitions\",\"financial_markets\",\"economy_fiscal\",\"economy_monetary\",\"economy_macro\",\"energy_transportation\",\"finance\",\"life_sciences\",\"manufacturing\",\"real_estate\",\"retail_wholesale\",\"technology\"]},{\"name\":\"time_from\",\"type\":\"string\",\"required\":false,\"description\":{\"en\":\"Start time in YYYYMMDDTHHMM format (e.g., 20220410T0130).\"}},{\"name\":\"time_to\",\"type\":\"string\",\"required\":false,\"description\":{\"en\":\"End time in YYYYMMDDTHHMM format.\"}},{\"name\":\"sort\",\"type\":\"string\",\"required\":false,\"description\":{\"en\":\"Sorting method for results.\"},\"enum\":[\"LATEST\",\"EARLIEST\",\"RELEVANCE\"]},{\"name\":\"limit\",\"type\":\"integer\",\"required\":false,\"description\":{\"en\":\"Maximum number of results (up to 1000).\"}}],\"examples\":{\"sample_parameters\":{\"function\":\"NEWS_SENTIMENT\"}},\"provider_description\":\"Alpha Vantage provides realtime and historical financial market data through a set of powerful and developer-friendly data APIs and spreadsheets. From traditional asset classes (e.g., stocks, ETFs, mutual funds) to economic indicators, from foreign exchange rates to commodities, from fundamental data to technical indicators, Alpha Vantage is your one-stop-shop for enterprise-grade global market data delivered through cloud-based APIs, MCP servers, spreadsheets, and more.\",\"stats\":{\"avg_execution_time_ms\":538.66,\"success_rate\":0.734}},{\"tool_id\":\"eodhd.sentiments.retrieve.v1.c2c27d35\",\"name\":\"Retrieve Sentiment Data\",\"description\":\"Get sentiment scores for one or more financial instruments (stocks, ETFs, crypto) calculated from news and social media, normalized on a scale from -1 (very negative) to 1 (very positive).\",\"params\":[{\"name\":\"s\",\"type\":\"string\",\"required\":true,\"description\":{\"en\":\"One or more comma-separated tickers, for example: AAPL.US,BTC-USD.CC\"}},{\"name\":\"from\",\"type\":\"string\",\"required\":false,\"description\":{\"en\":\"Start date for filtering sentiment data (YYYY-MM-DD)\"}},{\"name\":\"to\",\"type\":\"string\",\"required\":false,\"description\":{\"en\":\"End date for filtering sentiment data (YYYY-MM-DD)\"}}],\"examples\":{\"sample_parameters\":{\"s\":\"AAPL.US,BTC-USD.CC\"}},\"provider_description\":\"Access historical end-of-day stock prices, intraday data, US stock options, and real-time prices with free and advanced plans. EODHD provides financial data for 150,000+ tickers, including stocks, ETFs, funds, and currencies worldwide.\",\"stats\":{\"avg_execution_time_ms\":1240.63,\"success_rate\":0.779}},{\"tool_id\":\"alphavantage.news_sentiment.query.v1.467a92c0\",\"name\":\"Market News & Sentiment Trending\",\"description\":\"This API returns live and historical market news & sentiment data from a large & growing selection of premier news outlets around the world, covering stocks, cryptocurrencies, forex, and a wide range of topics such as fiscal policy, mergers & acquisitions, IPOs, etc.\",\"params\":[{\"name\":\"function\",\"type\":\"string\",\"required\":true,\"description\":{\"en\":\"The function of your choice. In this case, function=NEWS_SENTIMENT\"},\"enum\":[\"NEWS_SENTIMENT\"]},{\"name\":\"tickers\",\"type\":\"string\",\"required\":false,\"description\":{\"en\":\"The stock/crypto/forex symbols of your choice. For example: tickers=IBM will filter for articles that mention the IBM ticker; tickers=COIN,CRYPTO:BTC,FOREX:USD will filter for articles that simultaneously mention Coinbase (COIN), Bitcoin (CRYPTO:BTC), and US Dollar (FOREX:USD) in their content.\"}},{\"name\":\"topics\",\"type\":\"string\",\"required\":false,\"description\":{\"en\":\"The news topics of your choice. For example: topics=technology will filter for articles that write about the technology sector; topics=technology,ipo will filter for articles that simultaneously cover technology and IPO in their content. Below is the full list of supported topics: Blockchain: blockchain, Earnings: earnings, IPO: ipo, Mergers & Acquisitions: mergers_and_acquisitions, Financial Markets: financial_markets, Economy - Fiscal Policy (e.g., tax reform, government spending): economy_fiscal, Economy - Monetary Policy (e.g., interest rates, inflation): economy_monetary, Economy - Macro/Overall: economy_macro, Energy & Transportation: energy_transportation, Finance: finance, Life Sciences: life_sciences, Manufacturing: manufacturing, Real Estate & Construction: real_estate, Retail & Wholesale: retail_wholesale, Technology: technology.\"}},{\"name\":\"time_from\",\"type\":\"string\",\"required\":false,\"description\":{\"en\":\"The time range of the news articles you are targeting, in YYYYMMDDTHHMM format. For example: time_from=20220410T0130. If time_from is specified but time_to is missing, the API will return articles published between the time_from value and the current time.\"}},{\"name\":\"time_to\",\"type\":\"string\",\"required\":false,\"description\":{\"en\":\"The time range of the news articles you are targeting, in YYYYMMDDTHHMM format.\"}},{\"name\":\"sort\",\"type\":\"string\",\"required\":false,\"description\":{\"en\":\"By default, sort=LATEST and the API will return the latest articles first. You can also set sort=EARLIEST or sort=RELEVANCE based on your use case.\"},\"enum\":[\"LATEST\",\"EARLIEST\",\"RELEVANCE\"]},{\"name\":\"limit\",\"type\":\"string\",\"required\":false,\"description\":{\"en\":\"By default, limit=50 and the API will return up to 50 matching results. You can also set limit=1000 to output up to 1000 results.\"}}],\"examples\":{\"sample_parameters\":{\"function\":\"NEWS_SENTIMENT\"}},\"provider_description\":\"Alpha Vantage provides realtime and historical financial market data through a set of powerful and developer-friendly data APIs and spreadsheets. From traditional asset classes (e.g., stocks, ETFs, mutual funds) to economic indicators, from foreign exchange rates to commodities, from fundamental data to technical indicators, Alpha Vantage is your one-stop-shop for enterprise-grade global market data delivered through cloud-based APIs, MCP servers, spreadsheets, and more.\",\"stats\":{\"avg_execution_time_ms\":939.67,\"success_rate\":0.908}}],\"search_id\":\"7a7bae74-3990-43a6-aca6-3e1da69b4110\",\"elapsed_time_ms\":307.06}"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":5827,"aggregated":"{\"query\":\"Alpha Vantage NEWS_SENTIMENT relevance\",\"total\":3,\"results\":[{\"tool_id\":\"alphavantage.news_sentiment.query.v1.7aca3c4a\",\"name\":\"Market News & Sentiment\",\"description\":\"Returns live and historical market news & sentiment data from global news outlets covering stocks, crypto, forex, and economic topics.\",\"params\":[{\"name\":\"function\",\"type\":\"string\",\"required\":true,\"description\":{\"en\":\"The function to call. In this case, NEWS_SENTIMENT\"},\"enum\":[\"NEWS_SENTIMENT\"]},{\"name\"